  

<h5 id="reckless-index-sweep"><a href="https://ellanew.com/2025/10/08/inktober-reckless" title="wikilink"><span class="small-caps">⬅️</span> <span class="small-caps">RECKLESS</span></a> · <a href="https://ellanew.com/2025/10/01/inktober-index" title="wikilink"><span class="small-caps">INDEX</span></a> · <a href="https://ellanew.com/2025/10/10/inktober-sweep" title="wikilink"><span class="small-caps">SWEEP</span> <span class="small-caps">➡️</span></a></h5>
<p><img src="https://cdn.blot.im/blog_177bc256f0ee469c998e912e20ece048/_image_cache/afeb9957-8b7b-43f6-a4ed-747f02e8ea64.png" alt="minimalist line drawing of a person trying to hold a mass of dark, heavy, cloud-like substance from falling on them. Their limbs are trembling with the effort. Two other concerned, caring characters with a small heart drawn on their chests are helping the central character to hold up the mass. In the background are two additional characters running toward those in the foreground. There is also a sun just peeking its way over the horizon on the far left of the page." width="2116" height="1430"></p>
<p><em>Ink on paper, drawn with non-dominant hand</em></p>
<hr>
<p>A burden shared is a burden lightened! Those helping do not need to know what is inside the dark cloud, just that their friend is finding it too heavy to carry on their own.</p>
